text: 7/1 move in.. GATED resort-like luxury condo across from renown UCSD campus, next to UTC. 2 master suites. Granite counters, recessed lights, plantation shutters, laminate wood floor. Patio faces courtyard and is near the swimming pool. Awesome amenities! Take cooking classes in the gourmet kitchen. Two pools, spas, cabanas, gyms, dance/yoga studios. Biz Center, Reception hall, sports room, private theater. Near Jacobs Community Center, Marriott Hotel, Regents Medical Plaza; Westfield-UTC mall, shops and restaurants. Two side-by-side parking spaces near the elevator. A highlight of this extraordinary community is the Regents Clubhouse. a fabulous space for entertainment with a reception room, sports bar, four television monitors and one big-screen TV. Residents can reserve the chef-inspired dining area for a special evening with family or friends. Before or after a delicious dinner, enjoy a movie in the private screening room with stadium-style seating, high-back rocking chairs.

text: One of a Kind Condo in Little Italy! This unique unit located at the Village Walk on the 5th floor, unfurnished or furnished @ $4, 250.00, spacious living, loft style 2 story condo, 1 primary bedroom ensuite, plus 2nd full bath, in the heart of San Diegos Little Italy! With 26'ft ceilings, open living & dining area with beautiful wood flooring, opens up to a balcony facing India Street, partial views of the bay, city lights and the star of India. Unit offers a full kitchen with built in appliances, gas stove top range, oven, dishwasher, disposal, microwave, refrigerator, large walk in pantry, tile flooring, granite counters, bar style seating, and in unit laundry. Special feature of 2 areas/spaces on the first floor that can be used for a full-size home office and/or additional dining perfect for entertaining! Includes 1 garage assigned parking space; trash & recycle, garage storage unit, Village Walk communal space with kitchen, gym and several communal spaces in and around the courtyard.Tenant responsible for all utilities and renters insurance.
